# Env schema sync

Changing `src/shared/config/env-schema.ts` or `.env.example`? Run **[env-schema-add](../skills/env-schema-add/SKILL.md)** — decide Secret vs Variable, place under the right `.env.example` half, run `pnpm tool:sync-env-example`, keep GitHub Environments in sync. `NODE_ENV` is `development | production` only (no runtime branching).
